a particular purpose.

00:10:19.306 --> 00:10:29.076
So, it is a pilgrimage, in a way, that we are here. That we have to
look after our Mahalakshmi principle of our ascent.

00:10:33.076 --> 00:10:38.787
As you know, this ascent starts at the Nabhi

00:10:38.787 --> 00:10:42.655
and is surrounded by the Guru principle.

00:10:43.041 --> 00:10:49.008
Now the Guru principle within us, if it is
absurd, if it is a juxtaposition,

00:10:49.008 --> 00:10:55.363
placed in a juxtaposition where, if it is not properly
embedded within us,

00:10:55.363 --> 00:11:00.379
if it is not emitting through our character and behaviour,

00:11:00.379 --> 00:11:02.827
Mahalakshmi tattva cannot be strengthened.

00:11:02.827 --> 00:11:06.942
Mahalakshmi tattva is strengthened through Guru principle.

00:11:06.942 --> 00:11:11.690
Now we are lucky today because

